S2K will market the Funds to Intermediaries that:
(a) are registered as “broker-dealers” with the SEC, FINRA, and any other applicable jurisdiction in which they operate;
(b) will enter into an agreement with the Distributor to sell shares of the Funds to investors (copies of which shall be made available to S2K);
(c) will sell shares of the Funds through representatives in accordance with the then-current applicable Prospectus.
